edom'' (1909) *''An Empress in Love'' (1910) *''The Heart of Noel'' (1910) *''The Caxborough Scandal'' (1910) *''Clutterbuck's Treasure'' (1910) *''Peter the Great: A Novel'' (1911) *''Gubbins Minor, and Some Other Fellows'' (1913) *''Nathalia: A Tale'' (1913) *''A Bespoken Bride'' (1914) {{colend}}
