{{Infobox model | birth_date = {{birth date and age|1986|6|12}} |birth_place = [[Shoreham-by-Sea]], [[England]] |occupation = model |years_active = 2009-present |spouse = [[Sacha Kljestan]] }}
'''Jamie Lee Darley''' (born [[Shoreham-by-Sea]], [[England]], June 12, 1986<ref>[https://www.imdb.com/name/nm3724165/ Bio at IDMb]</ref> is an American model known for competing in the 2009 [[Victoria's Secret Fashion Show]] Model Search.
==Career== In 2009, Darley took part in Victoria's Secret Fashion Show Model Search to find a new "runway [[Victoria's Secret Angels|Angel]]" and placed second, losing out to [[Kylie Bisutti]].<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.nydailynews.com/lifestyle/fashion/2009/12/02/2009-12-02_kylie_bisutti_bests_jamie_lee_darley_to_win_victorias_secret_model_search_makes_.html |title=Kylie Bisutti bests Jamie Lee Darley to win Victoria's Secret Model Search, makes runway debut |first=Olivia |last=Smith |work=[[Daily News (New York)|Daily News]] |date=December 2, 2009 |accessdate=October 13, 2010}}</ref> During the competition, she posed for a lingerie shoot with the brand, took part in the Angels' media tour, and although omitted from the final broadcast, walked the runway during the show's first taping.<ref name="WAG">[http://www.nydailynews.com/sports/worldcup2010/galleries/the_hottest_wags_of_the_2010_world_cup/the_hottest_wags_of_the_2010_world_cup.html The hottest WAGs of the 2010 World Cup, Photo 9 of 41]</ref>
She has also appeared as a background character on the [[HBO]] [[Television program|show]] ''[[Entourage (U.S. TV series)|Entourage]]''<ref name="imdb">{{IMDb name|id=3724165}}</ref> as a limo driver for the character Turtle. She shot for Affliction's spring 2010 campaign alongside Dominic Purcell.<ref>[http://wn.com/affliction_spring_10_photo_shoot_featuring_dominic_purcell_and_jamielee_darley "Affliction Spring 10 Photo Shoot Featuring Dominic Purcell And Jamielee Darley", WN.com]</ref> She appeared in a [[Carl's Jr]] commercial.<ref>{{cite web |title=Jamie Lee Darley |url=https://issuu.com/831mag/docs/win-sp-2010 |website=Issuu |publisher=831 (via Issuu) |accessdate=26 September 2018}}</ref> She made her editorial debut in the March issue of [[Elle (magazine)|Elle Belgium]].<ref>[http://nl.elle.be/Fashion/Nieuws/Victoria-Secret-angel-Jamie-Lee-in-ELLE-Belgie "Victoria Secret angel Jamie Lee in ELLE België", Elle Belgium, 18/2/2011]</ref>
She is signed to [[Elite Model Management]].<ref>{{cite web |title=La WAG de la MLS de la semana: Jamie Lee Darley |url=https://us.as.com/us/2018/03/09/album/1520629767_799251.html |website=AS USA |publisher=AS USA |accessdate=26 September 2018}}</ref>
== Personal life == Darley was born in Shoreham, England. She immigrated to America with her family at a young age. She attended University of California, Santa Barbara where she played volleyball.<ref>[http://ucsbgauchos.cstv.com/sports/w-volley/mtt/darley_jamie00.html Bio at UCSB volleyball web page]</ref>
Darley is married to American soccer player [[Sacha Kljestan]].<ref name="WAG"/>
